# Project rules

- Use bun as package manager and for commands
- Prefer arrow functions over function declarations

## Frontend

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Use Shadcn UI for components
- Use Next.js for routing
- Use React for the frontend
- Use TypeScript for the frontend
- Use React.FC for components
- When installing shadcn components, do NOT override existing ones
- Never hardcode any text in components, use the translations file instead
- Components props must, unless exported, always be called 'Props'
- Always declare a const 't' for the useTranslations hook and dont give other names
- All frontend code must be mobile responsive, mobile is the primary format
